	(text "Rad_EN is logic low enable to change to low power mode\nLeave floating or open for high power mode\nRad_PW is logic low for power down and high for power up\nRad_PTT \"0\" force the module to enter TX state; and \"1\" to Rx state\n*Before enter sleep mode, user need to pull low RXD Pin\nto prevent current leakage or poor reset in the next time."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 79.248 26.162 0)
